highlights.text: TimelessRemixes has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Tình đầu tan trong mưa (Blues Rock)” is the highest at #4.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 233 days straight.
“Khuôn Mặt Đáng Drill - rmx” by MingDnx and dxrcy is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 26 spots at #45.
